title: BIG FACTS feat. YOUNG BUCK & DRUMMA BOY
itunes:title: BIG FACTS feat. YOUNG BUCK & DRUMMA BOY
description:
Young Buck makes an appearance on BIG FACTS with Drumma Boy to discuss his history with CASH MONEY RECORDS, karma, fatherhood, writing records for 50 Cent, new BOMBS 3 project & more.

Buck also addresses rumors surrounding transgender situation as well as his run ins with Nashville rappers CUB and Allstar.

Drumma Boy speaks on brotherhood and loyalty as well.
